videos.description: Grant Williams gets deep position in the paint and goes up strong for a basket and a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Williams muscles for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield loses the ball and gets it right back for a jumper.
videos.headline: Schofield tracks down loose ball

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield intercepts the pass and races defenders up the floor for a one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Schofield outhustles Georgia

videos.description: Georgia's William Jackson penetrates into the lane and delivers a pass to Nicolas Claxton for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Claxton throws down emphatic two-handed slam

videos.description: Admiral Schofield drives baseline and kicks it out to Lamonte Turner, who drains a 3-pointer to give Tennessee its first lead since early in the first half.
videos.headline: Turner gives Tennessee the lead

videos.description: Admiral Schofield knocks down a turnaround jumper to give Tennessee a 3-point lead in the final seconds.
videos.headline: Schofield seals first SEC championship in 10 years for Tennessee

videos.description: Head coach Rick Barnes reacts to Tennessee clinching a share of the SEC regular-season title and a No. 2 seed in the SEC Tournament.
videos.headline: Barnes talks Vols' fight to win share of SEC title

videos.description: Tennessee forward Admiral Schofield discusses the Vols' motivation during the season as they grab a share of the SEC regular-season title.
videos.headline: Schofield: 'Awesome to get this accomplishment'

videos.description: The Vols go on a 9-3 run with less than four minutes remaining to escape the Bulldogs 66-61.
videos.headline: No. 16 Tennessee tops UGA to win share of SEC title
